Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She has returned to her home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, it will be without my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san probably went back to her clan in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect me from her clan,\N she's sacrificing her happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow Kanako-san to sacrifice her love so that I might live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a man would be unfit to lead the Natsume clan! {retranslated}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:22.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,By the power of the Natsume clan! {*}{He's swearing an oath on his clan's power (hence why he plays with his ear), not saying he'll use it. (Though he will.)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:36.61,Alternate,,0,0,0,,There is a family whose leader is said\N to inherit the Ear of the Golden Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.16,Alternate,,0,0,0,,the Natsume clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:43.40,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This power lets him bring about any fate he desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.12,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It allows him to make any woman submit to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.58,Alternate,,0,0,0,,He is Natsume Kiroemon the 45th! {Is there a way to make the capital i's more visible (i.e. with horizontal lines at the top and bottom)?}
