Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiroemon-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon? Natsume Kiroemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. He recently left Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He is most likely headed here, to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To think he would actually come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We will see just how powerful the new head of the Natsume clan truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin preparations at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okochi-sama told me the manager of Kanoya would meet us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Natsume Kiroemon-sama, the 45th head of the Natsume clan, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies for arriving late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I run a place called Kanoya in Gion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one meeting us? {landlady again}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we be on our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Miss Gordon is{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okochi-sama explained everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When we informed her of what we've discovered so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she immediately{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She said you should have some tea and relax at my tea house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She will be driving around for\N a while to learn the streets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what the tea houses of Gion are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Kanako-san is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiroemon-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drink some tea instead\N of rambling on about another woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was just wondering\N where Miss Gordon went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tea house called Kanoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That's where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff are very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:40.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,How do you like the taste of the Mina women?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do you feel loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do you feel isolated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:50.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,You will become our slave, Natsume Kiroemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Ear of the Golden Dragon, said to bring calamity upon our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Playtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wasting your life on pointless hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you all of my techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The head of the Natsume\N clan is still a whelp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to use your power's full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:21.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's nothing more than a goodnight kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never underestimate the power of head of the Natsume clan. {clan -> clan head. The Natsume clan on its own isn't a threat to them, only the head.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiro-sama.
