Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder the head\N of our clan fears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Most impressive,\N Natsume Kiroemon the 45th!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you all to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want Kanako back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,come to Kiyomizu Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyabi! I didn't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:55.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll use my luck for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume Kiroemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you use Kanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If she knew she was being used as bait for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she would take her own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You made her fall that deeply in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you trying to say, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see the power\N of the head of the Natsume clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how terrifying this power can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel Kanako's pain,\N and it infuriates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger courses through my every vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remove the seal now, anything could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your naivete and overconfidence will be your undoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can defeat me\N without using your power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed. You can still stand after taking all that poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you finished me off immediately, you might've had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can defeat me if I release the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I want to defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the man with a power that terrifies even the Mina clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue to attack me,\N you could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have yet to see my true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Miyabi, the one destined to live in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the true form of Miyabi of the Mina clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I disgust you?{It's a Titan!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My own parents abandoned me because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it grants me strength without peer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mina assassination \Nsquad adopted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this body, I could\N not live in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But that ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I kill you, I will be a high-ranking officer in the Mina clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will be able to live in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's no ordinary fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:05.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,There's a great sorrow in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging for your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to rescue the woman I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've wasted your time,\N Natsume Kiroemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value her life,\N reseal your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you've won?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyabi. You forget your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was meant to be my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no further need for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, Noriko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you defying me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You ugly beast of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do anything you want to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,Th-This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:11.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,He could control Japan with his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,but he sealed it for one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. You can have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just repaying a debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly a strong man, willing\Nto die to protect the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be most amusing\N to see how you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume Kiroemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove the seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Show her your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never wanted to kill anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt and kill others\N to satisfy your own greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a god couldn't change your wicked heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one path left for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can read your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, a defenseless woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:22:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the Mina clan will not work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mina woman can do more with her body than just bewitch men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My body... is my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can destroy your ear,\N you'll never use your power again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did Miyabi's moths poison his blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You called your subordinate "ugly."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, you are far uglier than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was so ugly about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call me,\N a woman of the Mina clan, ugly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm going\N to do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you could read my movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.05,0:24:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.38,0:25:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.35,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You don't have to go back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
